The driver told the police that the hijackers then drove him around the city before abandoning him in Kibiku area near Ngong.
Mr Thuku was not injured in the twilight incident. He, however, lost Sh110,000.
At the time of the incident, the car had the registration number KCN 117M.
Sources say the Justice Ndung'u was not in the car when the incident happened.
Police have since asked anyone with information regarding the incident to report to the nearest police station.



